import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Box, Grid, Paper } from '@mui/material';

const ServicesPage = () => {
  return (
    <Container className="container">
      <Box mt={4} mb={4}>
        <Typography variant="h2" align="center">Our Services</Typography>
        {/* Services Price Chart */}
        <Grid container spacing={4} mt={4} justifyContent="center">
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Paper elevation={3} className="service-category">
              <Typography variant="h5" align="center" gutterBottom>
                Manicure
              </Typography>
              <Box p={2}>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Regular Manicure - $15</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">French Manicure - $20</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Weekly Manicure - $22</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Color Gel - $40</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Color Gel French - $50</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Buffing - $20</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Polish Change - $12</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Spa Manicure - $40</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Kids Mani+Pedi - $30</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Dazzle Dry - $25</Typography>
              </Box>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Paper elevation={3} className="service-category">
              <Typography variant="h5" align="center" gutterBottom>
                Gel Set
              </Typography>
              <Box p={2}>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Full Set (Extend) - $100</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Fill-In - $65+</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">French Fill - $75</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Long Nail Extra - $10</Typography>
              </Box>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Paper elevation={3} className="service-category">
              <Typography variant="h5" align="center" gutterBottom>
                Powder
              </Typography>
              <Box p={2}>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Dip Powder - $45</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Acrylic Full Set - $50</Typography>
              </Box>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Paper elevation={3} className="service-category">
              <Typography variant="h5" align="center" gutterBottom>
                Pedicure
              </Typography>
              <Box p={2}>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Classic Pedicure - $30</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Spa Pedicure - $45</Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" align="center">Gel Pedicure - $50</Typography>
              </Box>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default ServicesPage;
